November 29, 2017 Kevin Meagher (kmeagher@ulb.ac.be)
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Release V01-06-02

- use const iterator to traverse mctree
- remove unneeded ROOT stuff from CMakeLists.txt
- remove old dox files
- script cleanup: remove TrashCan and Finish

March 24, 2017 Kevin Meagher (kmeagher@ulb.ac.be)
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Release V01-06-01

- Replace `OMKey::IsInIce()` with `I3OMGeo::find()`
- Replace `TVector3` with `I3Position` and remove ROOT dependency
- Add serialization dependency
- Code and documentation cleanup

